const statisticalRouter = {
  route: null,
  name: null,
  title: '数据统计',

  order: null,

  children: [
    {
      title: 'bug统计',
      type: 'view',
      name: 'bug',
      route: '/statistical/bug',
      filePath: 'view/statistical/bug.vue',

    },
    {
      title: '功能点统计',
      type: 'view',
      name: 'function',

    {
      title: '版本统计',

      icon: 'iconfont icon-tushuguanli',
    },
    {
      title: '人员管理',
      type: 'view',
      name: 'dev-manage',
      route: '/statistical/dev-manage',
      filePath: 'view/statistical/dev-manage.vue',

    }

}

export default statisticalRouter
